A simple dice wagering game played with bitcoins. 

For each bet, Jackpot Dice will throw a dice, giving you a 1 in 6 chance of winning 400% of your bet. You also have another 1 in 6 chance of winning 100% of your bet back! Wagers can be any amount from 0.01 BTC up to 1000 BTC.

##History

The site was announced on January 28th, 2011 (2.1) however the payout returns have changed since that announcement.  The site is the second wagering site operated by BitcoinBet.com

